iv. Credentials

hunter.io 
	20 free searches / month
	Email address patterns, names, job titles
	Can use results for username enumeration
		e.g. Outlook time delay for invalid user

Breach Parse
	1.4B Clear-Text Credentials - 	40GB
	github.com/philipperemy/tensorflow-1.4-billion-password-analysis
	Parse/search tool at https://github.com/hmaverickadams/breach-parse
		./breach-parse.sh @example.com output.txt

haveibeenpwned

theharvester
	theharvester -d example.com -l <limit # of results> -b <source(s), hunter.io req's API key> -f output.txt


